LocalizedProperties.ProductDescription: A simple yet powerful calculator that includes standard, scientific, programmer, and graphing calculator functionality, as well as a set of converters between various units of measurement and currencies. It's the perfect tool to help you complete your math homework, manage your finances, plot and analyze equations on a graph, and evaluate algebra, trigonometry, and complex math expressions!

Properties.PublisherCertificateName: CN=Microsoft Corporation, O=Microsoft Corporation, L=Redmond, S=Washington, C=US

Features: Simple and easy to use calculator for all the basics
Powerful scientific calculator for complex math
Base conversions in programmer mode for new and experienced programmers
Intuitive and powerful graphing mode for students to visualize math equations
Convert between hundreds of units across categories, like currency, volume, mass, speed, and power
LocalizedProperties.ReleaseNotes: Thank you for using Calculator! We have updated the Calculator app to the beautiful look of Windows 11! We have also added app theme settings so that you can set the app in a theme different from Windows. As always, we'd love to hear from you, so please let us know what you think about the latest update!
